N.Y. Comp. Codes R. & Regs. Tit. 9 ยง 5606.1 - Submission of internal controls

State Regulations

In addition to the requirements set forth in Part 5601 of
this Chapter, a registration applicant shall submit to the commission for
approval a written description of its initial system of internal controls that
meets the requirements set forth in this Part. Notes
